data.chText: 专制统治者；专制君主；暴君
data.enText: a ruler with great power, especially one who uses it in a cruel way
an enlightened despot (= one who tries to use his/her power in a good way)

data.chText: 至高无上的权力；专制统治

value.def: A despot is a ruler or other person who has a lot of power and who uses it unfairly or cruelly.
